{"tid":1641073,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"斥《入樽》作者井上雄彥「港獨」　大陸網民翻舊帳揚言杯葛","createTime":"2019-10-09T08:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T09:58:52.000Z","uid":216021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"29ced9b00a37a7924348b4b9c61afafc22fb4afe","tid":1641073,"uid":216021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:34:22.000Z","msg":"美國 NBA 籃球隊候斯頓火箭總經理莫雷（Daryl Morey）日前於 Twitter 上支持香港反送中運動，引發大批中國球迷不滿抵制。風波未見平息，更有蔓延之勢。 《男兒當入樽》作者漫畫家井上雄彥今年 6 月在 Twitter 「按讚」兩條香港遊行的帖子，也被中國網民稱為「港獨」支持者，紛紛揚言杯葛。<br />\n<br />\n漫畫家井上雄彥今年 6 月 10 日，即 6 月 9 日一百萬人遊行之後，對出生於四川、現居日本的評論員石平太郎有關香港遊行的帖子「按讚」。石平太郎的原帖內容指，中國共產黨剝奪香港市民的自由和人權，激發逾百萬人上街遊行「決一死戰」。他又稱，事件反映中共統治下的「悲劇」與「絕望」，呼籲支持香港人，捍衛文明社會的自由和平。<br />\n<br />\n三日後，即「612 金鐘衝突」之後，井上雄彥在 6 月 13 日向自由民主黨眾議院議員河野太郎的帖子「按讚」。河野太郎的原帖指，得悉多名港人受傷，「非常擔心香港朋友的情況」，「希望問題通過和平討論解決，情況早日得到改善，維持香港的自由和民主」。<br />\n昨日起，「NBA風波」 爆發之後，微博開始有網民截圖批評井上雄彥在 6 月時這兩則「按讚」紀錄。大部分人一口咬定，井上雄彥「按讚」的行動即是「支持港獨」，甚至出現「井上雄彥港獨」的 hashtag。不少人更揚言與井上雄彥「割蓆」，紛紛揚言杯葛，「無論多愛櫻木花道和流川楓，中國人才是我的身份。再見了，灌籃高手，永別」、「你說你們安安靜靜的賺點錢不行嗎，你高興我們也高興，何必呢」、「最愛的漫畫，作者是歲數大了腦子糊塗了嗎！居然支持暴亂！是缺錢了來炒冷飯了吧，就當他去世了吧，漫畫也停留在最好的時光，拒絕炒冷飯！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E6%96%A5-%E5%85%A5%E6%A8%BD-%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E4%BA%95%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%84%E5%BD%A5-%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%BF%BB%E8%88%8A%E5%B8%B3%E6%8F%9A%E8%A8%80%E6%9D%AF%E8%91%9B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%2596%25A5-%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%25A8%25BD-%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BA%2595%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%259B%2584%25E5%25BD%25A5-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E8%2588%258A%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E6%258F%259A%25E8%25A8%2580%25E6%259D%25AF%25E8%2591%259B%2F&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=98c59cf2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%2596%25A5-%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%25A8%25BD-%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BA%2595%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%259B%2584%25E5%25BD%25A5-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E8%2588%258A%25E5%25B8%25B3%25E6%258F%259A%25E8%25A8%2580%25E6%259D%25AF%25E8%2591%259B%2F&h=2585cac3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/%E6%96%A5-%E5%85%A5%E6%A8%BD-%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E4%BA%95%E4%B8%8A%E9%9B%84%E5%BD%A5-%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%BF%BB%E8%88%8A%E5%B8%B3%E6%8F%9A%E8%A8%80%E6%9D%AF%E8%91%9B/</a>"},{"pid":"81f966696e1630afc349ce54ccde621a7b668dbc","tid":1641073,"uid":216021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8OT68Gj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8OT68Gj.png&h=550f5287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZcDu6s1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZcDu6s1.png&h=379237e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b4d9f2e943867d67a48a2c1be24797350fd5522","tid":1641073,"uid":218659,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:37:27.000Z","msg":"本身就買開盗版 扮乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34922eef95c9aeb5aedb54178e2d3448ede7de59","tid":1641073,"uid":269515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">「Xinnie the Pooh」Challenge</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q3PNSB7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq3PNSB7.png&h=70fa4b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a4UBLW8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt